  "text": "where J.L = 1 if the categorization decision for X i was correct, otherwise J.L = -1 and the winning node wk min ( e ) will be shifted away from x i . This node adaptation is illustrated in Fig. 1 . Additionally e k min ( e ) is the node-dependent learning rate as proposed in [CITATION_1] .",
